  "title": "Senior Embedded Software Engineer (Satellite Systems)",
  "description": "<h3>About the Role</h3><p>We are looking for a Senior Embedded Software Engineer to develop and support mission-critical satellite systems. This role covers the full embedded software lifecycle, from design and implementation to validation on target hardware, working closely with system architects and multidisciplinary engineering teams.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><p><ul><li>Design, develop, and unit test embedded software using C/C++.</li><li>Verify and validate software on target hardware.</li><li>Support software maintenance and deployed systems.</li><li>Improve system performance, reliability, and scalability.</li><li>Participate in future product definition and technical roadmap planning.</li><li>Mentor junior engineers and contribute to team development.</li><li>Drive high engineering standards and innovation culture.</li></ul></p><h3>Requirements</h3><p><ul><li>Degree in Electrical, Computer Engineering, or related discipline.</li><li>5+ years of experience in embedded software development (RTOS and/or Linux).</li><li>Strong proficiency in C/C++ and low-level drivers (CAN, UART, SPI).</li><li>Understanding of unit testing and Agile development practices.</li><li>Ability to read schematics and hardware datasheets.</li><li>Strong communication skills and problem-solving mindset.</li><li>Interest in space, satellite, or remote sensing systems.</li></ul><p><strong>To Apply</strong></p><p>To apply or find out more information on this role, please email us or send in your updated resume to:<br /><a href=\"https://www.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/job/general-management/assistant-export-control-manager-star-career-consulting-b2246758d92b888acc7acec3fd2c4c67#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lynn.tay@starcareerconsulting.com</a></p><p><strong>Lynn Tay</strong> (Reg. No. R1876711)<br /><strong>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD</strong> (EA Licence: 20C0353)</p></p>",
